 We have those, that of Saint Eusebius of Caesarea and that of Augustine of Hippo.

13
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:26,000
 See how Augustine of Hippo was looking on the Church and how to, what is the Church on the earth?

14
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:36,000
 You know that he wrote two cities, the God and the heavenly city, the God city and this state, the earth city.

15
