 So he wrote his two cities and he proposed some other, we can say, ecclesiology than that of Eusebius of Caesarea.

19
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:24,000
 This barbarians, which destroyed even his hippo and killed him, gave him a pessimistic outlook of the humankind, a potential to create a heavenly kingdom on the earth.

20
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:41,000
 Instead of returning to earth to its paradisical glory, Augustine acquired that it was the responsibility of the Christian Church to hold corrupt political actors accountable and to stand in the judgment against the inventable wickedness of the world.

